com.tofik.coolexoplayer.exoplayer

Class CoolExo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tofik.coolexoplayer.exoplayer.CoolExo

  • public final class CoolExo
extends java.lang.Object
    Global helper class to manage ExoCreator and SimpleExoPlayer instances. In this setup, ExoCreator and SimpleExoPlayer pools are cached. A Config is a key for each ExoCreator. A suggested usage is as below: 
    
 ExoCreator creator = CoolExo.with(this).getDefaultCreator();
 Playable playable = creator.createPlayable(uri);
 playable.prepare();
 // next: setup PlayerView and start the playback.
    Since:
    3.4.0

        @NonNull
public final com.google.android.exoplayer2.SimpleExoPlayer requestPlayer(@NonNull
                                                                                   ExoCreator creator)
        Request an instance of SimpleExoPlayer. It can be an existing instance cached by Pool or new one. The creator may or may not be the one created by either getCreator(Config) or getDefaultCreator().
        Parameters:
        creator - the ExoCreator that is scoped to the SimpleExoPlayer config.
        Returns:
        an usable SimpleExoPlayer instance.
